modName: theRoadstrokers Royal Elven Set White Brown Retexture
summary: This is a Retexture of the original File "theRoadstrokers Royal Elven Set" in white-brown color. (Original Mod is Required)
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#ff7700]ABOUT[/color][/b]


This is my first ever Retexture... i have never ever touched a pic even less a texture before, but 2 hours of Gimp Tutorials brought this to life, it took me like 3 hours with trials and errors.



[b][color=#ff7700]REQUIREMENTS[/color][/b]


You need the Original armor mod "theRoadstrokers Royal Elven Set" to use this retex:

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25083



[b][color=#ff7700]INSTALL[/color][/b]


After you installed the original Royal Elven Set, just unpack this file into DATA folder located inside Main Skyrim Folder, replace any files as prompted.
